snippet.title: Garuda Emblem Official Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo available now on itch.io for PC 
https://team-batalion.itch.io/garuda-emblem

Garuda Emblem is a 2D hand drawn free roam beat 'em up where you can explore the world, talk to people, do a quest and beat some enemies. That day, Farid took an opportunity to visit his campus and meet some new people. But that day was a bad day for him . . .

Follow us at:
https://www.instagram.com/team_batali...
https://www.twitter.com/BatalionTeam
